Name: IfLogoutIsCancelAppStaysInSamePage
Description: Validates that, if the logout process is canceled, the app stays in the same page after the modal is closed.

Name: CartMenuDisplaysCorrectAmountOfItems
Description: Validates that the amount of items in the shopping cart matches the amount that was selected by the user.

Name: ValidateCartSubtotalsAndTotal
Description: Validates that the cart subtotal and total are calculated correctly

Name: LoggedInUserAppearsInNavigationBar
Description: Validates that, when the user is logged in, their name appears in the navigation bar.

Name: PriceInShopMatchPriceInCart
Description: Validates that the displayed price in the shop matches the price in the shopping cart

Name: CanFillInContactPageAfterLoggingIn
Description: Validates that, after loging in, a user can fill in the contact page.

Name: ValidateEmailFormatError
Description: Validates that an error message is displayed when the user enters an invalid email.

Name: ValidatePricingIsCorrect
Description: Validates that the pricing information is correct.

Name: ErrorsCanBeFixed
Description: Validates that the error messages disappear once the mandatory fields are filled.

Name: CanSubmitCleanForm
Description: Validates that a clean form can be successfully submitted.

Name: CanBuyAProductByRating
Description: Validates that a user can select an item based on the stars rating.

Name: UserCanLogout
Description: Validates that a user can log out.

Name: ValidateThereIsFeedbackForIncompleteForm
Description: Validates that, if a form is incomplete, a message asking the user to complete the form is displayed.

Name: MandatoryErrorsAreDisplayed
Description: Validates that error messages are displayed if the mandatory fields are left blank.
